ASM v 0.0 - Another Syntactic Monstrosity.

A sandbox programming language "because I can".
ASM is my ill attempt to make Lisp even more expressive.

For licensing info see LICENSE file.
For things needing attention see TODO file.
For language specs see lang directory:
    lang/TODO    - ASM spec TODO.
    lang/lexical - ASM language formal description.

Visit its homepage at http://idorobots.org/asm/


Building:

ASM requires D version 2.053+.
To compile type:

    $ make [dmd]

By default it uses GDC compiler to compile ASM, to use DMD add `dmd'.